  <properties>
    <title>Introduction</title>
  </properties>
  <body>
    <section name="Introduction">
      <subsection name="What is Urlrewriter?">
        <p>
          Urlrewriter is a redirect servlet Filter.
          The URL Rewrite Filter supports the following options:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>redirect - Requests matching the "conditions" and the "from" for this rule will be HTTP redirected</li>
          <li>forward - Requests matching the "conditions" for this "rule", and the URL in the "from" element will be internally forwarded to the URL specified in the "to" element.</li>
          <li>permanent-redirect - Redirect with 301 response code</li>
          <li>temporary-redirect - Redirect with 302 response code</li>
          <li>pre-include</li>
          <li>post-include</li>
          <li>proxy - The request will be proxied to the full url specified.</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
    </section>
    <section name="Project status">
      <p>
        See the <a href="http://forge.onehippo.org/gf/project/urlrewriter">forge project page</a>
      </p>
    </section>
